 from brian gothamcity jsc nasa gov brian donnell subject val one vs bel nine six six sti was re best radar detector nntp posting host hotspare arc nasa gov organization nasa arc information sciences division lines two zero in article tobias convex com allen tobias wrote i live in the backyard of the folks who make the stalker radar system the valentine one has saved me many many many times from the stealth revenue enhancement traps of the local area i have had all the major brand detectors and imho nothing else even comes close to the v one i hadn t heard of the valentine one before car driver and other auto magazines recommend bel detectors i was considering their latest the nine six six sti which picks up super wideband ka and laser as well it also avoids radar detector detectors although i really don t care about this since i doubt i ll be driving in virginia anytime soon or have any other states also made detectors iilegal how does the valentine one compare with the bel products brian donnell